OL,6,FLikewise, over the same period, the
OL,7,FPSNI saw the number of hoax calls it
OL,8,Fdeals with a year rise from 2,666 to
OL,9,Fmore than 4,400, which is an increase
OL,10,Fof 65%.
OL,12,FPSNI Chief Superintendent Gary
OL,13,FMcDonald and NIAS Assistant Director
OL,14,FMark Cochrane, spoke to UTV about the
OL,15,Fimpact calls were having on their
OL,16,Fability to do their job.
