OL,3,CRevealed: Hoax calls and the problem
OL,4,Cfacing our emergency services
OL,6,FThe Chief Superintendent said: "You
OL,7,Fget those prank calls where people are
OL,8,Fringing our contact centres through
OL,9,F999 to report some sort of crime or
OL,10,Fincident is taking place when it
OL,11,Fclearly is not, through to those calls
OL,12,Fwhere people are asking for takeaways
OL,13,Ffor taxi services.
OL,15,F"We have had people who are reporting
OL,16,Fthat ATM's aren't working."
