OL,3,CRevealed: Hoax calls and the problem
OL,4,Cfacing our emergency services
OL,6,FThe PSNI, as well as the Ambulance
OL,7,FService have be stretched thin in
OL,8,Frecent years and having to deal with
OL,9,Fhoax calls is another issue they could
OL,10,Fdo without.
OL,12,FMr McDonald added: "The challenges
OL,13,Fthat we are facing as an organisation,
OL,14,Fparticularly in the context of
OL,15,Fincreasing demand and much more
OL,16,Fcomplex demand.
OL,18,F"So we could really do without these
OL,19,F4000 hoax calls per year.
