OL,3,CRevealed: Hoax calls and the problem
OL,4,Cfacing our emergency services
OL,6,FHe said: "My message to the people who
OL,7,Fengage in this sort of behaviour is
OL,8,Fsimply to stop.
OL,10,F"In this emergency call space we are
OL,11,Fdealing with life or death situations
OL,12,Fwere seconds and minutes do count and
OL,13,FI would just ask them to pause and
OL,14,Freflect.
OL,16,F"What if it was a member of their
OL,17,Ffamily, their mum their dad their
OL,18,Fsister, a member of their community
OL,19,Fwho could not get the necessary
OL,20,Femergency response."
