OL,3,CRevealed: Hoax calls and the problem
OL,4,Cfacing our emergency services
OL,6,FHe also added how stressful it can be
OL,7,Ffor the call handlers who have to
OL,8,Fanswer hoax calls: "It is frustrating
OL,9,Ffor the professionals who work in our
OL,10,Fcontact centres.
OL,12,F"They are a great team of people that
OL,13,Fwork across three centres within the
OL,14,FPSNI, over 400 people who are
OL,15,Freceiving those 999 calls and 101
OL,16,Fcalls and they do a tremendous job, so
OL,17,Fit is frustrating for them."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/9
