OL,3,CRevealed: Hoax calls and the problem
OL,4,Cfacing our emergency services
OL,6,FNIAS Assistant Director Mark Cochrane
OL,7,FOutlined the problems caused by hoax
OL,8,Fcalls for the ambulance service: "I am
OL,9,Faware of a call where our call takers
OL,10,Fin the room have been giving CPR
OL,11,Fadvice while resources have been on
OL,12,Ftheir way only to arrive and find that
OL,13,Fthe person making the call is the only
OL,14,Fperson in the house."
OL,16,FMark added: "When someone is dealing
OL,17,Fwith a call which is not a call, there
OL,18,Fis always patients waiting on
OL,19,Fambulances and they can be the sickest
OL,20,Fof our patients.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/9
