OL,3,CRevealed: Hoax calls and the problem
OL,4,Cfacing our emergency services
OL,6,F"Because the whole time that they are
OL,7,Fengaged with that caller they could be
OL,8,Fdealing with genuine patients.
OL,10,F"As well as getting some much needed
OL,11,Fstand-down time as well because that
OL,12,Fis a struggle for us also.
OL,14,F"At a time where our resources are
OL,15,Fpushed to an absolute maximum so
OL,16,Fanything that can be done to avoid
OL,17,Fthat would be a big help to us."
OL,19,FThe PSNI are keen to point out that
OL,20,Fhoax calling can carry a fine of up to
OL,21,F#2,500 or six months in prison.
